  "title": "Sales Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Track project progress against schedule and budget. </p><p>Create and maintain project documentation, including technical reports and meeting\nminutes. <br /><br />Coordinate with vendors and subcontractors to ensure timely delivery of materials and\nservices. </p><p>Assist with on-site installation and commissioning of mechanical systems. </p><p>Perform quality checks on installed equipment and materials. </p><p>Identify and troubleshoot technical issues during construction. </p><p>Prepare purchase orders for mechanical components and equipment. </p><p>Evaluate vendor proposals and source materials based on specifications. </p><p>Conduct research on new technologies and materials relevant to mechanical engineering\nprojects. </p><p>Analyze engineering data to identify potential issues and propose solutions. </p>",
